{"tid":1178704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國外交部：與伊朗保持經貿往來不應受到干擾","createTime":"2019-05-30T14:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T15:38:48.000Z","uid":5195,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"42cc650143c55f3d9ee85dc60eeb945c0aa41f1b","tid":1178704,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:55:11.000Z","msg":"據報有一艘載有伊朗石油的油輪，或尋求停泊香港。美方官員警告，任何與該艘油輪做生意的實體，均可能違反美國針對伊朗的制裁。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，中國外交部回應相關報道，指中方一貫反對任何國家、在這兒主要是美國，依據自己的國內法，實施所謂「長臂管轄」和單邊制裁。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人陸慷表示，中國同伊朗保持著正常的合作關係和經貿往來，合理、合法，應當得到尊重，不應當受到干擾。"},{"pid":"61cac264cee58135f0845dba87f687f8d50cd8e0","tid":1178704,"uid":117276,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:57:01.000Z","msg":"美國快啲打柒支那啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太撚串"},{"pid":"ce0cd68d1eb74fdc5d7ea901279491c97eb81869","tid":1178704,"uid":26389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:04:04.000Z","msg":"中國-伊朗-巴基21世紀邪惡核心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9346b692466fb824e1299c0129d5e51e8ebadf4","tid":1178704,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"61cac264cee58135f0845dba87f687f8d50cd8e0","tid":1178704,"uid":117276,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T14:57:01.000Z","msg":"美國快啲打柒支那啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太撚串"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:05:32.000Z","msg":"打柒香港先啦"},{"pid":"474767e9d5edfe22346cd13731bf54549d8f1991","tid":1178704,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:09:54.000Z","msg":"隻輪間持有公司叫&quot;中國崑崙銀行&quot;咁呢就係中国國企黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69897a62caf56df550bb1cb2cc069c6c53adf090","tid":1178704,"uid":204929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T15:18:31.000Z","msg":"借個位喺度share白宮聯署網嘅聯署先(反送中條例)<br />\n記得簽完要去email verify<br